            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-157bb1994db7e256-d59a78 twpub-157bb1994db7e256-9882b5\"><blockquote class=\"extract\"><p class=\"calibre11\"><i class=\"calibre12\">“Marty's 2<sup class=\"calibre14\">nd</sup> Edition builds on an amazing base of knowledge and experience, and provides even more insights, lessons, and frameworks that are imperative to every product‐based company.”</i></p></blockquote></div>"
        },
