            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/157bb1994db7e256/text/000001318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-157bb1994db7e256-d59a78 twpub-157bb1994db7e256-9882b5\"><blockquote class=\"extract\"><p class=\"calibre11\"><i class=\"calibre12\">“Marty reminds us of the importance of</i> why <i class=\"calibre12\">we build products. The product mindset and focusing on our customers, builds better entrepreneurs, companies and better solutions for all of us. This mindset is the foundation of building successful product companies at any stage.”</i></p></blockquote></div>"
